fulltitle: Roy Hargrove - Rare documentary 1997 + North Sea Jazz 1996
description: Rare dutch documentary about Roy Hargrove. Contains extended footage from Roy's performance at North Sea Jazz Festival 1996 in The Hague with Charles Craig on piano, Gerald Cannon on bass, Karriem Riggins on drums, Miguel "Angá" Diaz on percussion, Ron Blake on sax.
